summary: An ordinance authorizing the dismissal of the suit to condemn, certain portions of Hyde Park, Magnolia Park, Minor's Addition, Dewey's Addition, Ladd's Addition, Hiawatha Park, Hiawatha Park No. 2, Seattle Tide Lands, and Section 22, and 23, Township 25 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; for park, drive, and boulevard purposes; and to change from commercial use to park, drive and boulevard uses of certain streets under Ordinance No. 24332, Cause No. 77749, insofar as the same affects certain property.
